{"tid":757076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用一招就可以呃到測謊機？英國專家：收緊肛門括約肌","createTime":"2018-07-26T13:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T19:24:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f7e8390cce060503b8c4fbc9b51f89d0403f4a16","tid":757076,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:38:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180726/58478713\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58478713&d=jma%2B45ki75eZYCc5IccR11KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=34b6d845\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180726%2F58478713&h=8826dfe9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180726/58478713</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180726/large/1532572285_d0b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180726%2Flarge%2F1532572285_d0b3.jpg&h=4c43e357&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不少電影或真人騷節目都會用上測謊機盤問目標，藉以得出真相，然而有測謊專家聲稱，有一個小技巧可騙過測謊機－－靠收緊肛門括約肌。<br />\n<br />\n一名1972年加入美國俄克拉何馬州警隊、後來接受測謊訓練並獲發證書的測謊專家威廉斯（Doug Williams）表示︰「我懷疑測謊機的效用，我知我可以控制呼吸來影響結果，但我不知道如何控制心臟及血壓。」<br />\n<br />\n他後來在朋友的分享中得到啓發︰「直到朋友告訴我一個影響因素，就是當他緊張時，會將肛門的括約肌收緊。」威廉斯想到只要收緊括約肌，便可影響心血管的測量結果，從而欺騙測謊機，「我試過親身接上測謊機，然後收緊肛門，像要停止所有腸臟活動&hellip;&hellip;結果心跳頻率自然地上升，皮膚電導反應（GSR）亦一同上升。」<br />\n<br />\n由於測謊機主要靠探測人的呼吸、心跳頻率、血壓及皮膚反應等來判定目標有否說謊，意味收緊肛門括約肌一定程度上可干擾測謊機的結果。不過威廉斯亦都表示，如果要騙過測謊機，或許要經過一系列收緊括約肌練習才有明顯成效。"},{"pid":"e250aa6bcdcc92af6ae8bb69e73c293ab7aacacc","tid":757076,"uid":5253,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:39:38.000Z","msg":"咁Gay佬一定呃唔到部機"},{"pid":"d6798504b26bf16bbb5adb787595c18bb69d0d97","tid":757076,"uid":14130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:39:54.000Z","msg":"一系列收緊括約肌練習"},{"pid":"b9ec2555a5c7683f67ce7811a912d9d74c82fa3b","tid":757076,"uid":48276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:40:02.000Z","msg":"收陰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b5c3ecc00ec82fbffaf75d39e29e33862ed1c7","tid":757076,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"07fc452ae30c06302ac1eb53f1b95003f466959e","tid":757076,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"過時<br />\n依家情報人員盤問已經有埋detect你有冇收菊花嘅儀器"},{"pid":"e28b7505d56c6c95277deaa0ea740e0994701efd","tid":757076,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T13:41:46.000Z","msg":"遲早測謊機都要加入臀部感測器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28e83057731ab972854fa39c7a397112c2025d7","tid":757076,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"唔怪得GTA5暗示CIA最中意插電筒落犯人菊花去逼供啦"},{"pid":"877b43bb40b65a53edc5421b359fe845f6dfcc9a","tid":757076,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:38:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19fff84c4a93943a403e049999c9798188be3ca2","tid":757076,"uid":164913,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:39:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8e6ee883a3e825c3a731ec1e58d4b36180f5f14","tid":757076,"uid":55913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:41:33.000Z","msg":"無用 肛門都會放個測謊機"},{"pid":"4c60fe2deb98f63e9dc7486d1b9ffbf29a773736","tid":757076,"uid":173397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c4718660eeda73e4a71a8c58b93e6b2db5fed21","tid":757076,"uid":96732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"有無人一邊睇個post一邊縮屎眼肌肉"},{"pid":"e855